<div class="guide-main-content">

<p class="guide-intro">Gong is the market leader in conversation intelligence and revenue intelligence. At approximately $1,400–1,600/user/year (plus a $5,000 platform fee), it is one of the most expensive tools in the sales tech stack. For teams that use it fully — call recording, deal intelligence, pipeline forecasting, and rep coaching — the ROI is well-documented. But Gong is overkill for many teams, and several alternatives deliver comparable value at a lower price or are better for specific use cases.</p>

<h2>When to Consider a Gong Alternative</h2>

