<thead>
<tr><th>If Your Priority Is...</th><th>Better Alternative</th><th>Why</th></tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>Revenue forecasting over call intelligence</td><td>Clari</td><td>Clari's forecasting is more advanced than Gong's</td></tr>
<tr><td>Sales enablement + coaching combined</td><td>Mindtickle or Highspot</td><td>Dedicated enablement platforms with coaching built in</td></tr>
<tr><td>Budget under $500/user/year</td><td>Salesloft Conversations or Chorus</td><td>Bundled conversation intelligence at lower per-user cost</td></tr>
<tr><td>Basic call recording only</td><td>Fireflies.ai or Fathom</td><td>Free or near-free for basic transcription needs</td></tr>
<tr><td>Already on ZoomInfo</td><td>Chorus (ZoomInfo CI)</td><td>Bundled with ZoomInfo at lower incremental cost</td></tr>
<tr><td>Team under 10 seats</td><td>Salesloft or Fireflies</td><td>Gong's $5K platform fee is not justified at small scale</td></tr>
</tbody>
